divs: Sighting Detailsout smoking looking at the tower in front of my apartment when i see 6 to 8 faded white objects slowly moving south.I called for someone to bring me my phone so i could get a picture or a video but everyone was upstairs.The objects were in military type formation came to an almost stop, kind of did a reverse for a couple seconds and back to the same direction.went in to get my phone and objects went out of sight over my roof before i could take a picture
